系统命令优化工具
=============================================================================
+----------+-----------------------+-----------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|advcpmv   |带进度条的cp/mv命令    |https://github.com/jarun/advcpmv         |README.md里有安装方法         |
+----------+-----------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------+

工具用法
=============================================================================
" -------------------------------------                    advcpmv
Note: advcpmv安装方法:
        (1) 下载advcpmv仓库,执行里面的install.sh 
            (1.1) 下载:
                    $ https://github.com/jarun/advcpmv.git
                  Note: 修改下install.sh里的部分内容后再执行(下载的advcpmv已经包含了path,install.sh里又下载了一遍,将下载语句注释掉即可)
            
                  install.sh需修改的代码如下:          
                      # curl -LO https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jarun/advcpmv/master/advcpmv-$ADVCPMV_VERSION-$CORE_UTILS_VERSION.patch
                      # patch -p1 -i advcpmv-$ADVCPMV_VERSION-$CORE_UTILS_VERSION.patch
                      patch -p1 -i ../advcpmv-$ADVCPMV_VERSION-$CORE_UTILS_VERSION.patch
            (1.2) 修改完后,执行install.sh
                    $ chmod +x install.sh
                    $ ./install.sh  
        (2) 将advcpmv/src目录下的cp和mv命令拷贝到/usr/local/bin中
                $ sudo cp advcp /usr/local/bin
                $ sudo cp advmv /usr/local/bin
        (3) 在.zshrc中添加别名:
                alias cp='/usr/local/bin/advcp -g'
                alias mv='/usr/local/bin/advmv -g'
        (4) 更新.zshrc
                $ source .zshrc
Usage:
    @与自带的cp/mv命令用法一样,但会增加进度显示
